0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=9btibrhytL2HOKSu5WuRwbH4epo%3D\" alt=\"\"><h4 level=\"4\" id=\"3-添加机器人\">3. 添加机器人</h4><p>进入刚才添加的应用，添加机器人</p><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/896e7162dd9c4701a5f7ed5d5c265399~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=6rnpA9%2F3K%2BAx3VysmNvPx1mnT%2FU%3D\" alt=\"\"><h4 level=\"4\" id=\"4-设置订阅方式为长连接\">4. 设置订阅方式为长连接</h4><p>这样你的服务器就算是内网，本地的都没有问题。</p><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ae411d92ec324466b34e038eee55ca39~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=MuNeP%2F2oBufn2mIyo0eLvS9%2FhXY%3D\" alt=\"\"><h4 level=\"4\" id=\"5-添加接收消息事件\">5. 添加接收消息事件</h4><p><em>不添加你的飞书就收不到机器人的回信。</em></p><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/fa64a0400b6a4a9481ce0ae79821ea7e~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=1Nk3%2B%2BzrsUhWA339F%2BIFgIUFKBE%3D\" alt=\"\"><h4 level=\"4\" id=\"6-添加卡片回传交互\">6. 添加卡片回传交互</h4><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/2b9458c0d6a2434ab0a18ac005da3818~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=TTaeJOjQEUp3VOSivj0czJqUGZE%3D\" alt=\"\"><p>首次添加时，直接替换以下的信息到你默认的模版上。</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">json</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-json\">\n<span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;scopes&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;tenant&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;contact:contact.base:readonly&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:chat:read&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:chat:update&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message.group_at_msg:readonly&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message.p2p_msg:readonly&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message.reactions:read&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message.reactions:write_only&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message:readonly&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message:recall&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message:send_as_bot&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message:send_multi_users&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message:send_sys_msg&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:message:update&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span> \n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;im:resource&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">&quot;user&quot;</span><span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;contact:user.employee_id:readonly&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">]</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-punctuation\" class=\"hljs-punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h4 level=\"4\" id=\"7-发布版本\">7. 发布版本</h4><p>以后每一次变更上面的配置，都需要重新发布。</p><p><em>点击创建版本或者更新版本</em></p><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/fea7a03dfd904f81b0429bcf00381ca5~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=WdUfL%2FaCeN27xGza3bUPop9asXQ%3D\" alt=\"\"><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"openClaw中配置大模型key和飞书机器人\">openClaw中配置大模型key和飞书机器人</h3><p>此时复制飞书机器人的的 <strong>App ID</strong> 和 <strong>App Secret</strong></p><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/aeb63c6e95d84189b41409e43f6c854f~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=XvjGvbfxiogHdPX5qX%2Fw8JO78Zo%3D\" alt=\"\"><p>接着回到Trae的输入框中，输入以下内容：</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">markdown</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-markdown\">帮我根据以下信息配置openclaw：\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">1.</span> 飞书应用的AppID是：xxx    ，  App Secret 是 ：XXX\n\n<span class=\"hljs-bullet\" class=\"hljs-bullet\">2.</span> 联通云上的baseUrl是： &quot;https://aigw-gzgy2.cucloud.cn:8443/v1&quot;, apiKey是：xxxxxxxx\n   它支持 MiniMax-M2.5、glm-5、kimi-k2.5、Qwen3.5-397B-A17B、Qwen3-235B-A22B 模型。\n  \n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"飞书内的机器人和openclaw配对\">飞书内的机器人和openclaw配对</h3><p>此时打开你的飞书，找到创建好的机器人，直接对话：</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><p>正常的话，机器人会回复以下内容：</p><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/1f42743669e24de6bac4055ad991d2fd~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=WOV0jcVTc9ZOa3oejB475Yh%2BY8w%3D\" alt=\"\"><p>此时需要复制最后一段内容，然后放到Trae中</p><blockquote><p>帮我执行：openclaw pairing approve feishu xxxxx</p></blockquote><p>成功后，就可以在你的飞书上自由的对话操作你的机器人了。</p><p></p><img src=\"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/ea21df7bbcf1443c838dd780e6bef224~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&amp;x-expires=1773456815&amp;x-signature=hWv1yYlN3qecW1zun1NOyn6pw3k%3D\" alt=\"\"><p>以上是关于配置的基本流程</p><script type=\"module\">const injectHtml = (root, html) => {\n  const iframe = document.createElement(\"iframe\");\n  const htmlContent = `<html><head></head><body>${html}</body></html>`;\n  iframe.style.width = \"100%\";\n  iframe.style.height = \"100%\";\n  iframe.onload = () => {\n    const doc = iframe.contentDocument || iframe.contentWindow?.document;\n    if (!doc) {\n      return;\n    }\n    doc.open();\n    doc.write(htmlContent);\n    doc.close();\n  };\n  root.replaceChildren(iframe);\n}\n  document.querySelectorAll('.playground')?.forEach(el=>{\n    const html = el.getAttribute('data-html');\n    if (html) {\n      injectHtml(el,html);\n    }\n    const indicator = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    indicator.className = \"indicator\";\n    const showCode = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    showCode.className = \"show-code\";\n    showCode.innerText = \"code\";\n    showCode.onclick = () => {\n      el.parentElement.classList.remove(\"preview-only\");\n    };\n    const showPreview = document.createElement(\"div\");\n    showPreview.className = \"show-preview\";\n    showPreview.innerText = \"preview\";\n    showPreview.onclick = () => {\n      el.parentElement.classList.add(\"preview-only\");\n    };\n    indicator.appendChild(showCode);\n    indicator.appendChild(showPreview);\n    el.parentElement.appendChild(indicator);\n    if (window.screen.width < 768) {\n      showPreview.click();\n    }\n  });</script>","cover":{"src":"https://p6-xtjj-sign.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-73owjymdk6/1253e31789f441e0bf111869d015dc1f~tplv-73owjymdk6-jj-mark-v1:0:0:0:0:5o6Y6YeR5oqA5pyv56S-5Yy6IEAg5LiH5bCR:q75.awebp?rk3s=f64ab15b&x-expires=1773456815&x-signature=1ObY2bs%2FuDgyIIGW1APRD3GlRLg%3D","alt":"","title":null},"id":"skill-install-openclaw","path":"/posts/skill-install-openclaw.json"}